net.minecraftforge.event.terraingen

Class DecorateBiomeEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.fml.common.eventhandler.Event
      • net.minecraftforge.event.terraingen.DecorateBiomeEvent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DecorateBiomeEvent.Decorate, DecorateBiomeEvent.Post, DecorateBiomeEvent.Pre

    public class DecorateBiomeEvent
extends Event
    DecorateBiomeEvent is fired when a BiomeDecorator is created.
    This event is fired whenever a BiomeDecorator is created in DeferredBiomeDecorator.fireCreateEventAndReplace(Biome).

    world contains the world that is being decorated.
    rand contains an instance of Random to be used.
    chunkPos contains the original chunk for the decorator.

    This event is not Cancelable.
    This event does not have a result. HasResult
    This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.TERRAIN_GEN_BUS.
